resources.string: This project was created as a learning exercise to get up to speed with Kotlin Multiplatform on Web and to serve as an example/demo for future projects. It uses Compose Mutliplatform to run the same Kotlin code across Web, Android, and iOS.

Kotlin: %1$s
 Kotlin Multiplatform
 Compose Multiplatform
 Navigation Compose
This project was built by initially following tutorials and adding my own experiments and ideas.
